query:
SELECT 'utm_links' as table_name, id, destination_url as data FROM utm_links WHERE LOWER(destination_url) LIKE '%test%' OR LOWER(utm_source) LIKE '%test%' OR LOWER(utm_campaign) LIKE '%test%'
UNION ALL
SELECT 'socials', id, nom FROM socials WHERE LOWER(nom) LIKE '%test%'
UNION ALL
SELECT 'content_types', id, nom FROM content_types WHERE LOWER(nom) LIKE '%test%'
UNION ALL
SELECT 'objectives', id, nom FROM objectives WHERE LOWER(nom) LIKE '%test%'
UNION ALL
SELECT 'audiences', id, nom FROM audiences WHERE LOWER(nom) LIKE '%test%'
UNION ALL
SELECT 'channels', id, nom FROM channels WHERE LOWER(nom) LIKE '%test%';
